https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7RB11xd8fX9CttXCNnaQkneQa3v.jpg World War II is raging on the Eastern front but the soldier Nikanor has been sent to Siberia: bot as a prisoner, but as the leader of a motley group of entertainers who travel from village to village giving concerts. Still, Big Brother is watching and when the entertainers encounter a strange man in the woods there is trouble brewing. One of the performers falls in love with the mysterious backwoodsman, but the secret service is after him, too. Agitprop Team 'Kill the enemy!'
